# Support Policy for Furfect Match

Welcome to Furfect Match Support! We’re here to help you resolve any issues and ensure you have the best possible experience using our app.

---

## Contact Information

If you need assistance, please contact our support team:

- **Email:** furfectmatchco@gmail.com
- **Response Time:** Within 48 hours

For faster assistance, please include:
- Your device model and OS version  
- The version of Furfect Match you’re using  
- A brief description of the issue or question

---

## Scope of Support

We provide help with:
- Troubleshooting app errors, crashes, or bugs  
- Account or login issues  
- Questions about app features  
- Feedback and suggestions  

---

## What’s Not Covered

We may not be able to assist with:
- Problems caused by unofficial app versions or modified devices  
- Third-party integrations or services outside Furfect Match’s control  
- Requests unrelated to Furfect Match

---

## Feedback

We welcome your feedback!  
If you have ideas to improve Furfect Match, reach out to **furfectmatchco@gmail.com**.

---

Thank you for using Furfect Match!

